_source.text: Adrian Doyle, founder of the Blender Studios and Melbourne Street Art Tours, agrees saying our street art is "better than New York" but Jaklyn Babington, curator for international prints and drawings at the National Gallery of Australia, counters that while street art has been hugely popular internationally, "within Australia it's still growing out of its infancy".
